Spotlight Install and Configuration
=================================

Install RHEL 6.3
yum update

check java version = 1.7 +

useradd  spotlight
passwd spotlight2013

yum install java-1.7.0-openjdk.x86_64

postgresql
h2
tomcat tomcat-webapps tomcat-admin-webapps
grails 2.1.1  or grials 2.2.0
imagemagik
xml
xsl



